1- Requirements:
----------------
 Operating System		:	LINUX (tested on Fedora-8 and lower versions)

 Compiler/Interpreter/Librarie(s):	g++, Perl and SSF API's

2. FAQ's for INSTALLATION
-- ----------------------

 2.1) Error: test.sh: line 5: shallow_parser_hin: command not found
      
      Export the PATH variable properly. Check INSTALL for that.

